thread.title: LEAH

author: LEAH
title: LEAH
text: I left ordering invites late, after searching high and low in stores I found nothing. Ordering was quick and easy with so much variety. Option for priority printing a plus but not needed, invites were sent the day after I ordered and I've had nothing but compliments from those receiving them. With three children and plenty of party's to plan I will definetly be using paper Divas again!
